Actress Iyabo Ojo has blasted a blog for insinuating her daughter is in an intimate relationship with a guy in Dubai. It all started when Buga crooner, Kizz Daniel and her daughter sparked rumours after they were spotted in a video having a nice time together in Manchester, UK. The blogger, in an attempt to refute the claim, alleged that Priscillia was in an amorous relationship with a guy in Dubai. Responding to these claims, Iyabo Ojo in Yoruba language cursed the blogger   IK Osakioduwa tests Deyemi Okanlawon to recreate…     I’ve lived to carry AMVCA trophy – Taiwo…     Tearful Saskay gets car as birthday gift from fans   She said: “Whoever wrote & sent this post oni fi owo yen se owun re re mo….. ogun i la ra lo ma ba ti e je……..shonponu lo mo pa e wo ati iyalaya e pelu baba nla baba e danu, ogun la fi e je re we, gbogbo awon ti won ba fe gbe ogun ti awon omo temi, Iyabo Ojo. e ma so fo e mi danu, ase gun ….e kere si number wa ….. elo po si wa eti po to” Which is translated to mean: “You will not use your hand to achieve good things. May the God of Iron deal mercilessly with you. The god will kill you, your mother, and your great grandfather. “The god of thunder will soak your blood and to those that want to wage war against me Iyabo Ojo, you will lose your life, amen You are not enough, go and get back up.”